### ========================================
### STATION ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### 1. Get Station (PUBLIC - No auth required)
# @name getStation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Update Station (PROTECTED - Auth required)
# @name updateStation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Super Radio",
  "slogan": "La mejor música las 24 horas",
  "streamUrl": "https://stream.superradio.com/live",
  "websiteUrl": "https://www.superradio.com",
  "logoUrl": "https://www.superradio.com/logo.png",
  "facebookUrl": "https://facebook.com/superradio",
  "instagramUrl": "https://instagram.com/superradio",
  "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/superradio",
  "youtubeUrl": "https://youtube.com/@superradio",
  "tiktokUrl": "https://tiktok.com/@superradio",
  "country": "Argentina",
  "state": "Buenos Aires",
  "city": "Buenos Aires",
  "postalCode": "C1001",
  "phone": "+54 11 1234-5678",
  "whatsapp": "+54 9 11 1234-5678",
  "email": "contacto@superradio.com",
  "address": "Av. Corrientes 1234, CABA, Argentina",
  "dayStartTime": "06:00"
}

### 3. Update Station - Partial (solo algunos campos)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/station
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slogan": "Tu compañera musical",
  "streamUrl": "https://stream2.superradio.com/live"
}

### 4. Update Station - Social Media Only
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/station
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "facebookUrl": "https://facebook.com/superradio.oficial",
  "instagramUrl": "https://instagram.com/superradio.oficial"
}

### 5. Update Station - Contact Info Only
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/station
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+54 11 9876-5432",
  "whatsapp": "+54 9 11 9876-5432",
  "email": "info@superradio.com",
  "address": "Av. Santa Fe 4567, CABA, Argentina"
}

### 6. Update Station - Change Day Start Time
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/station
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayStartTime": "06:00"
}
